elements.name: Verifying Admin or SuperAdmin Add a new user

steps.name: I am on the Add User page
I enter "Abhishek" in the Name field
I enter "abhishek.gaur12@example.com" in the Email field
I enter "12345ABC6789" in the Mobile No. field
I enter "Gorakhpur" in the City field
I enter "A brief about Abhishek" in the About user field
I select "Admin" from the User Role dropdown
I enter "Gaur@123" in  Password field and enter "Gaur@123" in the Password (Confirm) field
I check the Visibility features toggle
I attach "\images\images.png" to the Upload Image field
I click the create user button
